title: Maloney and Desmond back 10cc star Godleys WholeWorld Band
text:
Maloney and Desmond back 10cc star Godley's WholeWorld Band 
Independent.ie Sunday 25th October, 2015 
Barry Maloney, the former Digifone boss turned hugely successful tech investor, and billionaire financier Dermot Desmond have led a near EUR2m funding round for WholeWorldBand, the innovative music creation and sharing site developed by 10cc drummer Kevin Godley.
